Describes how to migrate WordPress users from one website to another.

Shows how to export WooCommerce customers to CSV, Excel, or XML.

Explains how to import WooCommerce customers.

Describes how to migrate WooCommerce customers from one website to another.

Shows how to execute custom code to modify import user data on the fly.

